'''Ruwa''' (''rural area'' in English) inzvimbo isina kuvakwa dhorobha kana kuti guta. Kumaruwa kunonyanya kuitwa mabasa ekurima mbesa, kuchengeta zvipfuyo, nokurima miti.

Chikamu chinosvika 60% ye[[hugari]] hwevanhu MuZimbabwe vanogara kumaruwa.

